@base = {{host}}/api
@token = {{token}}
@avatarFileId = 1

### 1) 注册成功
POST {{base}}/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1001",
  "educationEmail": "test1001@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 2) 用户名重复（预期：业务异常）
POST {{base}}/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1001",
  "educationEmail": "test1001@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 3) 邮箱重复（预期：业务异常）
POST {{base}}/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test2",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1003",
  "educationEmail": "test1001@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 4) 登录成功（预期：code=0，data 为 LoginRespVO，包含 token 和 userInfo）
POST {{base}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5) 管理员登录（预期：code=0，data 为 LoginRespVO，包含 token 和 userInfo）
POST {{base}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 6) 登录失败（预期：code=405，message=密码错误，data=null）
POST {{base}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "1234567"
}

### 7) 获取当前用户（带 token，预期：code=0）
GET {{base}}/account/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) 获取当前用户（不带 token，预期：code=406）
GET {{base}}/account/my

### 8.1) 上传头像图片（预期：code=0，返回 fileId；手动填入 @avatarFileId）
POST {{base}}/file/upload?fileType=AVATAR
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_pass.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ../images/test_pass.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### 9) 修改昵称和头像（文件绑定方式，预期：code=0）
POST {{base}}/account/my/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nickname": "测试用户1001-修改",
  "fileID": {{avatarFileId}}
}

### 10) 修改邮箱（预期：code=0）
POST {{base}}/account/my/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "educationEmail": "test1001_new@nuist.edu.cn"
}

### 11) 修改密码（预期：code=0）
POST {{base}}/account/my/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "12345678"
}

### 12) 修改密码缺参数（预期：code=422）
POST {{base}}/account/my/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newPassword": "12345678"
}

### 13) 旧密码错误（预期：code=405）
POST {{base}}/account/my/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "wrong_old_password",
  "newPassword": "12345678"
}
